00:27.011 --> 00:29.234
And for you who are listening and can't see it,

00:29.474 --> 00:32.880
I basically, and I'm full Mickey experienced.

00:33.621 --> 00:36.986
I got ears, I've got the shirt, except it's lucky the rabbit.

00:37.267 --> 00:38.408
That's a whole different conversation.

00:38.429 --> 00:41.233
If you don't know about him, you can go Google him connected to Disney.

00:41.253 --> 00:41.754
Here's the point.

00:43.076 --> 00:46.802
We were at Disney like five weeks ago, six weeks ago as a family, and at an epic time.

00:46.982 --> 00:50.007
And I've shared this about food and other things, but let me begin like this.

00:50.809 --> 00:52.371
