19:02.971 --> 19:04.593
We need to remind you of something.

19:04.693 --> 19:05.874
Hey, we grew up with you.

19:07.810 --> 19:09.292
I mean, they said, is this not Jesus?

19:10.453 --> 19:13.557
The son of Joseph, whose father and mother we know?

19:13.577 --> 19:17.122
How can he now say, I came down from heaven?

19:17.902 --> 19:19.224
Please, Jesus, we know you.

19:20.205 --> 19:21.347
We went to parties with you.

19:22.008 --> 19:23.249
We were at weddings with you.

19:24.330 --> 19:25.492
We've hung out and been in your house.

19:25.512 --> 19:27.354
We know your mom and dad, Joseph and Mary.

19:27.635 --> 19:29.357
We know everything you're saying is false.

19:29.417 --> 19:30.138
You're one of us.

19:30.999 --> 19:32.220
We lived with you for years.

19:32.440 --> 19:33.342
Yes, you're different.

19:33.362 --> 19:33.642
Sure.

19:33.682 --> 19:36.946
You do some miracles, but man, this is going to your head.

19:37.890 --> 19:40.353
Jesus is returning, stop grumbling among yourselves.

19:41.976 --> 19:45.180
No one can come to me unless the Father who sent me draws them.

19:46.042 --> 19:47.564
And I'll raise them up on the last day.

19:48.064 --> 19:49.066
Yes, yes, yes, fine.

19:49.807 --> 19:54.153
You hung out with me and you know my parents and we grew up together, but that's not the whole story.

19:54.173 --> 19:55.295
So you cannot come to me.

19:55.335 --> 20:00.562
You will always hang out with me and look at me, but you will miss me because actually you're blind.

20:01.346 --> 20:08.755
Yes, I'm the guy you played soccer with, and yes, I'm the guy that swam on those hot summer days, but before all of you were, I am.

20:10.757 --> 20:11.979
See, this is where he's driving.

20:13.020 --> 20:18.627
Jesus says in verse 45, as it's written in the Old Testament prophets, they will all be taught by God.

20:18.827 --> 20:22.031
Everyone who listens to the Father and learns from him comes to me.

20:23.032 --> 20:30.962
Jesus says to this whole crowd, including a lot of his old friends, if you don't accept me, and what I teach when I claim it about with yourself, myself,

20:31.586 --> 20:35.111
You actually don't know God, you're not hearing from God, you're not taught by God.

20:35.472 --> 20:37.655
Okay, whoa, just every pause for a moment.

20:38.917 --> 20:41.441
Think about every religious person on earth who's not a Christian.

20:42.382 --> 20:53.699
Jesus says, if you do not accept what I claim about myself and what I teach and who I am, you do not know God and God does not hear from you and you're not even being taught by God.

20:54.500 --> 20:55.261
Oh my goodness.

20:57.084 --> 21:01.330
And just by the way, in case anyone's missing it, Jesus says, I'm offering

21:02.914 --> 21:06.078
Amazing things, but let me say this in emphatic terms.

21:07.139 --> 21:10.884
No one has seen the Father, God, except the one who is from God.

21:11.765 --> 21:12.746
Only he has seen the Father.

21:13.747 --> 21:15.009
I tell you the truth.

21:15.029 --> 21:16.831
He who believes has everlasting life.

21:17.632 --> 21:19.715
I am the bread of life.

21:20.636 --> 21:23.319
Your forefathers ate manna in the desert and they died.

21:24.441 --> 21:28.826
But here is the bread that comes down from heaven, which a man may eat and not die.

21:28.866 --> 21:29.607
He points to himself.

21:30.809 --> 21:31.890
I am the living bread.

21:32.034 --> 21:34.016
That came down from heaven.

21:34.797 --> 21:36.518
If anyone eats this bread, they'll live forever.

21:36.558 --> 21:40.042
This bread is my flesh, which I will give for the life of the world.

21:40.362 --> 21:41.984
See, Jesus wants to do something.

21:42.644 --> 21:46.008
Most of us never thought or would think God wants to do.

21:46.829 --> 22:00.402
Jesus intentionally divides the crowd, allowing those who are truly being drawn to get closer and actually pushing many, many farther away to leave, to reject, to run from Jesus and never return.

22:01.410 --> 22:03.774
Jesus says, look, you have to ingest me.

22:03.794 --> 22:04.795
Take me in.

22:04.855 --> 22:05.576
You will live.

22:06.097 --> 22:07.058
You must eat my flesh.

22:07.139 --> 22:15.130
Now, just as a side note, a lot of people, especially the Roman Catholic Church, will say, this is a reference to communion, the Lord's Supper.

22:15.811 --> 22:18.175
That's why they teach at every service, right?

22:18.215 --> 22:19.056
You take communion.

22:19.096 --> 22:21.740
You literally eat the body of Jesus.

22:21.840 --> 22:27.128
But see, the word flesh is never used by Paul or the gospel writers when talking about communion.

22:27.449 --> 22:30.994
And oh, by the way, communion or Eucharist, it doesn't even exist yet.

22:32.002 --> 22:39.257
This is a metaphor where Jesus is inviting people not only to think about him, but to embrace him, to receive him internally.

22:40.760 --> 22:43.365
Now, the Jews began to argue sharply among themselves.

22:43.386 --> 22:45.390
How can this man give us flesh to eat?

22:45.470 --> 22:47.153
Now, the crowd turns, of course, on each other.

22:47.193 --> 22:48.416
They misunderstand Jesus.

22:48.436 --> 22:49.458
They begin to fight.

22:49.570 --> 22:52.594
Are we really supposed to literally eat his flesh and drink his blood?

22:52.635 --> 22:53.456
This is offensive.

22:53.836 --> 22:54.738
This is cannibalism.

22:54.798 --> 22:55.619
This is sinful.

22:55.719 --> 23:02.429
If Jesus had a PR director, by the way, or a social media manager, they would be losing their mind and freaking out right now.

23:02.789 --> 23:04.352
This is a PR nightmare.

23:04.873 --> 23:07.797
We would want Jesus to soften his statement or clarify.

23:08.117 --> 23:09.199
And he goes, no, I'm not clarifying.

23:09.239 --> 23:10.200
Let me actually go further.

23:11.863 --> 23:13.365
Now, why is Jesus being so direct?

23:13.405 --> 23:14.066
So harsh.

23:14.498 --> 23:22.107
because he wants to kill any notion about himself and God that is false because those things actually become idols and lead to death, not life.

23:23.289 --> 23:31.619
I almost wonder if Jesus at this moment stopped and pondered before he said these next words, knowing that from a human perspective, he was able to lose so much that he had worked for.

23:31.659 --> 23:34.783
Jesus said to them, I tell you the truth.

23:35.784 --> 23:41.812
Unless you eat the flesh of the son of man and drink his blood, you have no life in you.

23:42.793 --> 23:43.634
Okay, back to Disney.

23:44.258 --> 23:47.285
You can follow all the best best Instagram accounts I've been Disney.

23:47.325 --> 23:50.071
You can follow all the TikTok bloggers that are there.

23:50.391 --> 23:59.090
You can watch all the documentaries, but you only cross into real knowing when you go and experience the same with Jesus.

24:00.322 --> 24:02.204
Jesus will not take back anything he said.

24:02.244 --> 24:03.966
He said, you must accept me, ingest me.

24:04.326 --> 24:05.667
I must literally be inside you.

24:05.908 --> 24:07.950
You don't just know about me, you must meet me.

24:08.150 --> 24:13.395
Eat and drink in Greek, by the way, are written as a once-for-all action, not doing it again and again.

24:13.435 --> 24:14.677
You must accept me.

24:14.717 --> 24:19.181
And of course, this is pointing to Jesus' life, death, and resurrection.

24:20.663 --> 24:23.105
The call is to truly have Jesus in your life, to be changed by him.

24:23.526 --> 24:27.570
There's one guy I read years ago on this who I just love what he said, what he said, look.

24:28.258 --> 24:31.403
Is Jesus real to you spiritually something you can taste or handle?

24:33.326 --> 24:38.414
Is Jesus as much a part of you as that what you eat?

24:39.495 --> 24:45.425
Don't think me being blasphemous when I say he must be as real and useful to you as hamburgers and fries, but he is asking.

24:46.366 --> 24:56.562
I say this because obviously Jesus is far more real and unusual than fries or burgers, but the unfortunate thing is that for many people he is much less than fries or burgers.

24:58.626 --> 25:06.461
Jesus is intentionally setting up a great divide, pointing to those that have taken him in and those that know about him, but will not experience or know him.

25:07.503 --> 25:12.212
Jesus says it again, verse 54, who ever eats my flesh and drinks my blood has eternal life.

25:12.713 --> 25:14.075
I'm going to raise them up on the last day.

25:14.777 --> 25:17.742
For my flesh is real food and my blood is real drink.

25:18.664 --> 25:21.810
Whoever eats my flesh and drinks my blood remains in me and I remain in them.

25:22.850 --> 25:28.601
Just as the living father sent me, I live because of the father.

25:28.861 --> 25:31.686
So the one who feeds on me will live because of me.

25:32.989 --> 25:34.432
This is the bread that came down from heaven.

25:35.293 --> 25:40.563
Your forefathers ate manna and died, but he who feeds on this bread will live forever.

25:41.705 --> 25:42.446
I'm the only way.

25:43.028 --> 25:44.370
I'm the only thing that will last.

25:44.546 --> 25:47.751
You have to accept me, accept my teaching, accept my claims of being from heaven.

25:48.031 --> 25:49.774
You have to accept my coming work on the cross.

25:50.115 --> 25:51.537
Then and only then will you live.

25:51.777 --> 25:53.480
Only then will you be given eternal life.

25:53.840 --> 25:55.763
The problem isn't intellectual here.

25:57.105 --> 26:02.213
The crowd begins to see that Jesus is really getting them to a place, to a corner.

26:03.215 --> 26:05.718
They now begin to see the call and the command and the cost.

26:05.738 --> 26:06.880
Things become very clear.

26:07.261 --> 26:13.330
And the heavier the image that Jesus uses, the stronger and stranger it gets, and the more they realize.

26:13.570 --> 26:14.491
how serious this is.

26:15.032 --> 26:16.655
See, let me just pause and do this again.

26:16.835 --> 26:22.344
At this moment, Jesus is making a huge PR mistake from our perspective.

26:23.105 --> 26:27.672
Jesus and the disciples had tens of thousands of followers.

26:27.913 --> 26:30.076
Everything was up and to the right, up and to the right.

26:31.018 --> 26:32.640
Now, here's the truth.

26:33.882 --> 26:38.770
Some of them were deeply committed, some were on the fringe, some in the middle, some really far away, but see,

26:38.946 --> 26:41.750
Jesus is looking for genuine disciples, not just crowds.

26:42.071 --> 26:46.698
He knows people follow him for a million reasons, but they really don't want to meet him.

26:46.738 --> 26:52.326
It's temporal, it's fickle, it's like the good news falling on dry and rough ground.

26:52.346 --> 26:54.269
They say yes, but they have no discomfort.

26:54.750 --> 26:57.934
They say we like Jesus as we see him or as we want him.

26:57.974 --> 27:01.480
But Jesus is basically saying, you can't put words into my mouth.

27:01.520 --> 27:05.325
You cannot reshape me to suit your ideas or politics or wants.

27:05.405 --> 27:06.727
No, no, no, no.

27:07.028 --> 27:07.649
I'm Savior.

27:07.829 --> 27:08.530
I'm Lord.

27:08.770 --> 27:12.236
I'm in charge, never you, only me."

27:13.578 --> 27:14.780
Well, how did the crowd respond?

27:15.401 --> 27:21.071
Well, verse 66, from this time forward, many of his disciples turned back and they no longer followed Jesus.

27:23.536 --> 27:28.404
Then Jesus turns to his inner group.

27:28.424 --> 27:30.628
Do you want to leave me to Jesus said to the 12?

27:30.808 --> 27:34.194
And Simon Peter answered, listen, Lord, to whom shall we go?

27:34.946 --> 27:36.929
I mean, you have the words of eternal life.

27:36.969 --> 27:39.792
We've come to believe and to know you are the Holy One of God.

27:39.812 --> 27:41.254
I'm stuck with you, Jesus.

27:42.616 --> 27:44.098
I love Peter's work here.

27:44.198 --> 27:48.064
I've checked it all out and I have no other place to run.

27:48.264 --> 27:48.845
Nothing's better.

27:48.865 --> 27:50.186
Nothing's more satisfying yet.

27:50.266 --> 27:55.654
Listen, there is a ton of options out there, but you're still the best option.

27:55.674 --> 28:00.760
Now, by the way, if you haven't caught it yet, let me tie the beginning, the middle and the end of this sermon together with the whole summer.

28:02.102 --> 28:04.946
Jesus through this whole passage is claiming to be divine.

28:06.082 --> 28:09.387
Remember, some of you might not know this, some of you do.

28:09.467 --> 28:13.533
When Moses met God, personally for the first time, it was at the burning bush.

28:15.156 --> 28:20.344
And when Moses realizes that God's presence is in front of him, Moses says something to God.

28:20.424 --> 28:22.046
He says, what is your name?

28:23.509 --> 28:26.233
And God says out of that burning bush, I am that I am.

28:26.293 --> 28:31.060
This is a variation of one of the names we looked at, week one, Yahweh.

28:32.482 --> 28:34.866
And it basically means he who is

28:34.978 --> 28:36.179
and he who causes to be.

28:37.841 --> 28:39.663
Now, if you haven't caught it, here it is.

28:40.223 --> 28:45.949
Jesus keeps saying, I'm from heaven, I'm from heaven, I existed before I existed, and I am the bread of life.

28:46.670 --> 28:48.091
I came from heaven.

28:48.151 --> 28:53.937
And this gets even clear, crystal clear, two chapters later.

28:55.559 --> 29:00.363
In chapter eight of John, he's talking to some religious, I think some religious leaders.

29:01.585 --> 29:03.026
And this is what he said, lean in,

29:04.162 --> 29:08.908
Jesus says he yet, he himself is Jewish, he's speaking to Jewish people and Jewish religious leaders.

29:09.008 --> 29:13.554
Your father Abraham rejoiced at the thought of seeing my day.

29:13.594 --> 29:17.339
He was glad, he saw it and he was glad.

29:19.201 --> 29:24.368
The people say back to Jesus, you're not yet 50 years old and you've seen Abraham?

29:26.190 --> 29:32.018
Very truly, I tell you, before Abraham was born, I am.

29:33.218 --> 29:37.805
And at this they picked up stones to stone him because Jesus, but Jesus himself slipped away.

29:38.346 --> 29:41.571
Jesus explicitly, I'm the bread of life, I am.

29:41.591 --> 29:45.857
I am equal of God, for I am God, I am divine.

29:47.319 --> 29:48.942
Now, here are the gospels given.

29:48.962 --> 29:50.905
The good news is given to all of us.

29:52.207 --> 29:53.649
I think this is one of the best ways to look at it.

29:53.729 --> 29:56.213
We're not denying there are a thousand other options out there.

29:56.373 --> 29:59.277
Secular, spiritual, religious, filling on the blank.

29:59.898 --> 30:00.980
There are a million options.

30:01.020 --> 30:02.482
The buffet is vast,

30:02.562 --> 30:04.345
There's only one best option.

30:05.427 --> 30:06.188
This is the good news.

30:07.190 --> 30:09.554
Jesus, who is equal with the Father, has come down from heaven.

30:10.455 --> 30:11.477
He is the great I am.

30:12.419 --> 30:16.806
And if you truly and fully accept Jesus and His gift of life, you get saved.

30:17.788 --> 30:18.829
How do you eat this bread?

30:18.929 --> 30:19.871
How do you drink this cup?

30:20.152 --> 30:24.038
Jesus said it, that God is literally speaking to some of you right now.

30:24.759 --> 30:28.786
The work of God is this, to believe in the one He sent.

30:30.498 --> 30:33.642
You must accept and only accept Jesus, the bread of life.

30:35.264 --> 30:49.802
If you say, I believe in Jesus Christ, you're saying, I know him, I've met him, I trust him, I place my complete confidence in him, I admit I'm a sinner, I admit that I have much of my life believed I'm good enough or I don't need God or I'm religious enough.

30:50.423 --> 30:56.410
I would also admit that I have said to God, prove it or prove yourself or show up, then I'll believe in you.

30:57.592 --> 30:59.314
But now I actually need to say,

31:00.002 --> 31:01.143
I need bread that will last.

31:02.665 --> 31:06.249
And so I'm humbling myself and I'm saying, you are Lord and God and Savior.

31:06.330 --> 31:07.571
I welcome your forgiveness.

31:07.651 --> 31:09.413
I welcome you to run my life.

31:09.553 --> 31:10.955
I welcome your eternal life.

31:11.416 --> 31:12.317
I want to be held by you.

31:12.537 --> 31:13.298
I don't want to fear death.

31:14.459 --> 31:20.947
I now believe that everything I know about this life and what happens at my death and after depends on Jesus Christ.

31:22.169 --> 31:23.410
My question to all of you

31:24.258 --> 31:26.420
It's have you said yes to Jesus and what will you do?

31:26.480 --> 31:30.064
Will you say yes he is from heaven and the bread of life or will you be the crowd?

31:30.705 --> 31:33.388
Walk away, get angry or reject him.

31:35.870 --> 31:38.854
Many of us listening or watching this right now are hearing this.

31:39.054 --> 31:39.634
We're Christians.

31:41.056 --> 31:51.427
But it's an interesting moment for us to pause because that crowd is still found even among us who walk with Jesus.

31:52.648 --> 31:54.130
I'd like you to do something if you would

31:54.370 --> 31:58.894
mind right now, no matter where you are, this is not some weird manipulative new age moment.

31:58.914 --> 32:00.696
Let's just, could you just close your eyes?

32:03.058 --> 32:04.800
Could you close your eyes wherever you might be?

32:06.261 --> 32:14.549
And I want you to picture that massive crowd of 10,000 plus people and Jesus somewhere among that crowd or in front of the crowd.

32:15.751 --> 32:20.475
And I ask you, so remember Jesus lives in you and he's real and the Holy Spirit is in you.

32:21.936 --> 32:23.538
Ask the Holy Spirit to show you

32:24.002 --> 32:26.385
where you actually are in proximity to Jesus.

32:28.147 --> 32:39.321
Not where you used to be five years ago or two years ago or last month, where, from God's view, where are you at this moment in this season of life in your proximity to Jesus?

32:39.361 --> 32:39.761
Take a moment.

32:39.821 --> 32:41.724
I'm gonna pray Father and Son, Son, the Holy Spirit.

32:42.344 --> 32:43.466
Don't let the evil one speak.

32:44.367 --> 32:50.194
Don't let vain imagination just show people where they are in proximity to you.

33:03.938 --> 33:05.580
I mean, this is what I talked about last week.

33:07.462 --> 33:08.644
I'm not talking about salvation.

33:09.745 --> 33:11.667
We who are Christians are saved by His work.

33:11.728 --> 33:18.235
The point is not to invent how emotionally do I feel, how hyped up am I about Jesus.

33:18.336 --> 33:19.777
It just, how close am I?

33:20.638 --> 33:21.419
What's my proximity?

33:21.479 --> 33:29.049
I guarantee you hundreds of you literally in a vision in your head where you saw a crowd and there was Jesus in some way and you were like, wow, I'm really close to Him.

33:29.069 --> 33:30.130
I'm actually really far away.

33:31.650 --> 33:33.273
Your prayer this week needs to be Jesus.

33:33.893 --> 33:41.025
I actually want to be like the disciples and I want to move closer and be closer.

33:42.787 --> 33:44.971
I want to end this sermon very specifically.

33:44.991 --> 33:47.254
I was praying this week and had a sense I needed to share this.

33:48.196 --> 34:00.114
There's a few of you that are here and you have been long-term Christians or you've been Christians for a while and because of pain or life or intellect, you are

34:00.706 --> 34:02.888
really struggling with the Christian faith.

34:02.988 --> 34:08.133
Actually, some of you have prepared to leave the Christian faith or you have left the Christian faith in secret.

34:10.015 --> 34:14.920
And this is what I genuinely believe the Spirit of God is saying to some of you.

34:16.521 --> 34:17.683
Yes, there are many options.

34:19.084 --> 34:22.728
And you can leave and go away like many other people have.

34:24.389 --> 34:29.394
But if Jesus really actually is from heaven, and Jesus really is the bread of life,

34:30.146 --> 34:33.371
And Jesus really died and really actually physically rose from the dead.

34:33.391 --> 34:36.335
You will find nothing like him as you go exploring.

34:37.397 --> 34:38.298
Where else can you go?

34:38.318 --> 34:41.243
I love what Peter basically says.

34:41.283 --> 34:43.085
We've looked at the alternatives and they're hollow.

34:43.105 --> 34:43.927
They're not lasting.

34:44.227 --> 34:51.178
They don't even come close to Jesus' love, his holiness, his perfection, his consistency for someone or a small group of you hearing this today.

34:51.238 --> 34:56.025
You know literally right now, some of you are like, why is he looking at me?

34:56.566 --> 34:57.006
I'm not.

34:57.147 --> 34:59.410
I'm literally taping this and it's used alone in a room.

35:00.290 --> 35:01.752
This is divine conspiracy.

35:03.154 --> 35:07.399
God is cornering you on purpose, loving concern.

35:08.340 --> 35:16.210
So you will be brought back to the same place that you used to be in and that you will not just finish, but you're finished well.

35:16.330 --> 35:21.336
Peter says, and you should say this week, I'm stuck with you, Jesus.

35:22.458 --> 35:23.619
And I'm not just stuck with you.

35:23.739 --> 35:26.002
Oh, this, this is, this is the moment.

35:26.818 --> 35:29.742
Some of you literally got us saying this to you in this mode.

35:30.083 --> 35:31.545
I'm also stuck with your church.

35:32.626 --> 35:33.628
I'm stuck with your people.

35:33.668 --> 35:35.130
I'm stuck with your bride.

35:37.133 --> 35:40.798
Jesus is speaking very situationally right now.

35:40.958 --> 35:48.108
Would you come and meet with me once again and let me bring healing, life, restoration, and new starts?

35:50.451 --> 35:52.434
Lord, we're thankful for this whole summer series.

35:53.058 --> 36:00.308
We're really thankful that you've taught us who you are, what we can know about you, what we can't, what we should expect from you, how good you are, how holy you are, how kind you are.

36:00.768 --> 36:03.953
We thank you that all of who you are is found fully in Jesus.

36:04.794 --> 36:08.659
We thank you that Jesus, you're the bread of life that's come from heaven and so a few things.

36:09.039 --> 36:16.189
For those who are listening right now and watching right now who've not crossed the line of faith, you have to open their eyes and their hearts to you.

36:16.529 --> 36:19.954
God our Father and Lord Jesus Christ send the Holy Spirit to literally

36:20.098 --> 36:27.128
open people's eyes, show them their sin, show them their lostness, show them the holiness of what they trust in and lead them to Christ.

36:27.468 --> 36:31.334
Even in this moment, do this work we ask in Jesus' name.

36:31.354 --> 36:34.438
Remove the blinders of the evil and remove the deadness of the heart.

36:35.319 --> 36:37.182
Bring life in Jesus' name right now.

36:38.324 --> 36:48.498
For others of us, Lord, show us genuinely where we are with Jesus, not so we feel shamed or condemned, but actually bring us closer, closer, closer so we can walk.

36:50.178 --> 37:06.200
And lastly, for that small group of people who are denying and struggling and wondering and running and hiding publicly or privately, bring them to the place actually where they will want you as the best option again.

37:06.220 --> 37:07.762
We pray this in Jesus' name.

37:08.423 --> 37:09.044
We all sit together.

37:09.084 --> 37:10.706
Amen.

